chat.title: Electrolyte protocol
chat.message: Is the protocol going to be on a separate order item? We are missing a lot of it - e.g. checking potassium 2 hours after replacement done, checking magnesium 6 hours after replacement done. Also, noting that the "corrected calcium" formula has been shown to be inaccurate, are we planning on updating this to also include ionized calcium for a guide?
